{"attributes":{"title":"Slowest traces (top 20)","description":"Top 20 request_trace events by total_duration_ms (unfiltered -- pick a trace_id here, then edit the query bar in Trace detail table/Trace phase totals to drill into it). STALE SIGNAL, same request_trace family (794 requests, 2026-04-23 to 2026-06-07, silent 24+ days). FINDING: distribution is extremely right-skewed -- top traces run 4.7-18.8 minutes (1,128,878ms / 1,095,568ms / 921,288ms for the top 3), far above the ~29.8s average established in the sibling Request Timing dashboard. Cross-checked directly against ES: the top 3 slow traces (f5684891, 7941bb73, 44a2c00a) have 43/29/25 total_steps vs. ~11 steps for a typical trace, suggesting these are requests with unusually long tool-execution/retry sequences rather than measurement artifacts. An average-only view (like Total duration over time) hides this tail entirely.","visualizationType":"lnsDatatable","state":{"visualization":{"layerId":"1b14a58a-3c25-44cd-a727-2c204152039c","layerType":"data","columns":[{"columnId":"af0acb7c-39a3-4794-836a-3dd56ecfdc98"},{"columnId":"2b873132-67c4-4ae5-b78b-05cfe8a3bbb1"}]},"query":{"query":"event_type: \"request_trace\"","language":"kuery"},"filters":[],"datasourceStates":{"formBased":{"layers":{"1b14a58a-3c25-44cd-a727-2c204152039c":{"columns":{"af0acb7c-39a3-4794-836a-3dd56ecfdc98":{"label":"Top 20 values of trace_id","dataType":"string","operationType":"terms","sourceField":"trace_id","isBucketed":true,"params":{"size":20,"orderBy":{"type":"column","columnId":"2b873132-67c4-4ae5-b78b-05cfe8a3bbb1"},"orderDirection":"desc","otherBucket":true,"missingBucket":false,"parentFormat":{"id":"terms"},"include":[],"exclude":[],"includeIsRegex":false,"excludeIsRegex":false}},"2b873132-67c4-4ae5-b78b-05cfe8a3bbb1":{"label":"Total duration (ms)","dataType":"number","operationType":"max","sourceField":"total_duration_ms","isBucketed":false,"params":{"emptyAsNull":true},"customLabel":true}},"columnOrder":["af0acb7c-39a3-4794