{"attributes":{"description":"Trace one request end-to-end: pick a slow trace_id, then drill into its step-by-step breakdown. STALE SIGNAL, flagged prominently: request_trace/request_trace_step (794 requests, 9834 steps, 2026-04-23 to 2026-06-07) stopped emitting on 2026-06-07, 24+ days before this build. No replacement telemetry has been found. The original dashboard was also independently broken: the top-level references array had every entry duplicated (a copy-paste corruption), and its controls panel was bound to the legacy eabfafeb-... index-pattern instead of the canonical agent-logs-pattern. The original Single Trace Waterfall panel (5 overlapping metrics on one horizontal bar chart) is replaced here by two simpler, verified panels: Trace phase totals and Trace detail table. To inspect a different trace: copy a trace_id from Slowest traces, then edit the trace_id in the query bar of Trace detail table and Trace phase totals.","kibanaSavedObjectMeta":{"searchSourceJSON":"{\"query\":{\"language\":\"kuery\",\"query\":\"\"},\"filter\":[]}"},"optionsJSON":"{\"hidePanelTitles\":false,\"useMargins\":true}","panelsJSON":"[{\"embeddableConfig\":{\"enhancements\":{}},\"gridData\":{\"h\":15,\"i\":\"panel-1\",\"w\":48,\"x\":0,\"y\":0},\"panelIndex\":\"panel-1\",\"panelRefName\":\"panel_0\",\"title\":\"Slowest traces (top 20)\",\"type\":\"lens\",\"version\":\"8.9.0\"},{\"embeddableConfig\":{\"enhancements\":{}},\"gridData\":{\"h\":15,\"i\":\"panel-2\",\"w\":24,\"x\":0,\"y\":15},\"panelIndex\":\"panel-2\",\"panelRefName\":\"panel_1\",\"title\":\"Trace phase totals\",\"type\":\"lens\",\"version\":\"8.9.0\"},{\"embeddableConfig\":{\"enhancements\":{}},\"gridData\":{\"h\":15,\"i\":\"panel-3\",\"w\":24,\"x\":24,\"y\":15},\"panelIndex\":\"panel-3\",\"panelRefName\":\"panel_2\",\"title\":\"Trace detail table\",\"type\":\"lens\",\"version\":\"8.9.0\"}]","timeFrom":"now-90d","timeRestore":true,"timeTo":"now","title":"Request Traces","version":1},"references":[{"id":"rt-slowest-tra